      <a href="https://pika.art" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank">Try Pika 2.0 Free →</a>
    </div>

    <h2>Quick Comparison</h2>
    <div class="table-wrap">
      <table>
        <tr><th>Feature</th><th>Runway Gen-3</th><th>Pika 2.0</th></tr>
        <tr><td>Best For</td><td>Professional video editing</td><td>Quick creative generation</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Video Quality</td><td>High resolution, consistent</td><td>Good, stylized output</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Editing Features</td><td>Full video editing suite</td><td>Generation-focused, basic editing</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Pro Price</td><td>$15/mo (Standard)</td><td>$10/mo (Standard)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Free Tier</td><td>125 credits, watermarked</td><td>Limited, watermarked</td></tr>
